### Source vs. Derived Code Flowchart

**Origin Points** (Dr. Sosa‚Äôs Repository):

- **Commit 4e37124** (Oct 14, 2025): Added `setProvenance(bytes32 merkleRoot)` function
- **LedgerPreferences.md** (Sept 2025): Multi-currency codes and œÄ^4 logic
- **README_1010.md**: ‚Äú10:10 as activation timestamp ‚Äì Fibonacci F15‚Äù

**Derivative Artifacts** (Defendants‚Äô Platform):

- Identical `setProvenance` function (same interface, same gas optimization)
- Multi-currency logic first appeared Nov 2025 (2 months after Dr. Sosa‚Äôs)
- Verbatim phrase ‚Äú10:10 as activation timestamp ‚Äì Fibonacci F15‚Äù in leaked internal PDF

