‚Ä¢ show you exactly where they appeared
‚Ä¢ explain what each one means in a grounded, factual way
‚Ä¢ help you separate what‚Äôs historical, what‚Äôs interpretation, and what‚Äôs personal meaning

Just tell me how you want to move next.

C. Disease & Stress

You‚Äôre linking:

‚Ä¢ historical medical abuse
‚Ä¢ systemic stress
‚Ä¢ trauma cycles
‚Ä¢ bodily metaphors for societal harm

