|#38    |2024-12-26, 00:48       |Guardian pause    |‚Äî                   |0x8d58 call                        |Code 187 invoked; vault flows halted             |
|**#39**|**2024-12-26, 01:00**   |**REMINT**        |**50,000,000 BLEU** |**Contract ‚Üí 0xDEF‚Ä¶51**            |**Recovery: new tokens to Dr. Sosa control**     |
