How It Works Section:
‚Ä¢	Could be a simple 1-2-3 graphic:
1.	Estate ‚ûú Endowment: Court-approved trust conversion (with a tiny scales of justice icon).
2.	Endowment ‚ûú Scholars: Annual scholarships granted (graduation cap icon).
3.	Scholars ‚ûú Community: Graduates give back, build projects (community icon).
‚Ä¢	Also a note ‚ÄúPowered by MetaVault blockchain for transparency‚Äù with a little blockchain icon. Maybe even a live feed or embed showing the latest MetaVault entry (if possible) ‚Äì e.g., ‚ÄúVault Status: Funded ‚úÖ  Scholarships disbursed: 2 ‚úÖ‚Äù.

Live Vault Ledger (Transparency) Section:
‚Ä¢	A dynamic element (for launch, maybe a static placeholder) showing something like:
‚Ä¢	‚ÄúVault Balance: $X (updated in real-time)‚Äù
‚Ä¢	‚ÄúCurrent Scholars: [list of first cohort names]‚Äù
‚Ä¢	A clickable link ‚ÄúView Full Ledger‚Äù that would take users to the MetaVault explorer or a dedicated transparency page with detailed logs of funds (ensuring we showcase that nothing is hidden).

Testimonials/Quotes (future):
‚Ä¢	Placeholders for quotes from a community leader or a student (e.g., ‚ÄúThis fund changed my life‚Ä¶ - Future Scholar‚Äù or ‚ÄúA new model for education equality‚Ä¶ - Local Official‚Äù).

Call to Action Banner:
‚Ä¢	Mid-page banner with a powerful line: ‚ÄúJoin the journey. Be part of a living legacy.‚Äù
‚Ä¢	Buttons: Donate (if open to outside donations), Partner with Us (for institutions), or simply Contact Us.

Footer:
‚Ä¢	Quick links (Repeat navigation + Legal info).
‚Ä¢	Possibly logos of partners or relevant institutions (e.g., a university logo or EV0LBank logo as a tech partner).
‚Ä¢	Contact info and a disclaimer (‚ÄúRiccardo Mitchell Scholarship Endowment is a 501(c)(3) pending charitable trust‚Ä¶ etc.‚Äù).
‚Ä¢	Also a tiny note: ‚ÄúInscribed in MetaVault 51000 ‚Äì Transparency Guaranteed‚Äù with maybe an Ethereum or blockchain symbol.

Style & Feel:
‚Ä¢	The design should blend regal and futuristic. Colors perhaps royal blue or purple (trust, legacy) accented with gold (prosperity) and maybe circuits pattern or constellation (to hint at tech and guidance).
‚Ä¢	Font choices mixing something classical for headings (for gravitas) and clean modern font for body (for innovation).
‚Ä¢	Visual motifs: vault door, scroll manuscript, digital code, ancestral symbols ‚Äì harmonized in a sleek, responsive web design.

This homepage layout ensures that any visitor ‚Äì whether a student applicant, a curious community member, or a potential investor ‚Äì immediately grasps the Endowment‚Äôs purpose, uniqueness (sovereign + blockchain), and how to get involved. It‚Äôs informative, inspiring, and transparent, reflecting the cross-realm integrity of the project.         




+.PHONY: sync format format-check lint mypy pyright tests gen-docs build-docs serve-docs deploy-docs check

install:
	uv sync --all-extras --all-packages --group dev

format:
	uv run ruff format
	uv run ruff check --fix

format-check:
	uv run ruff format --check

lint:
	uv run ruff check

mypy:
	uv run mypy .

pyright:
	uv run pyright

test:
	PYTHONPATH=. uv run pytest

build:
	uv build

serve-docs:
	uv run mkdocs serve

deploy-docs:
	uv run mkdocs gh-deploy --force --verbose

check: format-check lint pyright test